recently tried Industry Pizza in Brooklyn, and unfortunately, I wasn’t too impressed. I had heard a lot of good things about the place, so maybe I just happened to catch them on a bad day. For starters, the bathrooms were out of order, which was a bit frustrating.\\n\\nI ordered my food to-go, and when I got it, the pizza was burnt and, to my surprise, a bit cold. Considering all the hype, I was expecting much better quality. The pricing is also a bit on the high side, especially for a regular slice — I’ve had better for less.\\n\\nOn the plus side, they are one of the few pizza spots that offer sparkling water, which I really appreciated. Pizza is absolutely worth the visit! These are photos from my visit in April. From the moment you arrive, you can tell it's a popular spot—there’s usually a crowd, and the line to order moves quickly. The atmosphere, both inside and outside, is fantastic, with a great vibe that makes it a fun place to hang out. The staff is incredibly friendly and welcoming, adding to the overall positive experience. Now, the pizza—oh my goodness! I had the pesto and cheese pizza, and it was pure magic. The crust was perfectly crispy, yet soft in all the right places, with just the right amount of chew. The pesto? Bold, fragrant, and fresh…it practically danced on my taste buds. The cheese was the real MVP oozing and perfectly melted, making each bite feel like a little slice of heaven. You can actually watch them work their pizza-making magic right in front of you, which is such a cool experience. Definitely recommend this pizza to anyone visiting New York.\",null,[0,240]]]],[null,null,null,null,null,\"https://business.google.com/local/business/14772176348859172102/customers/reviews/reply?p\\u003dCiRDaGREU1VoTk1HOW5TMFZKUTBGblNVUlFhMWxQY0hwblJSQUIQAA%3D%3D\",[null,null,null,\"/local/business/14772176348859172102/customers/reviews/reply?p\\u003dCiRDaGREU1VoTk1HOW5TMFZKUTBGblNVUlFhMWxQY0hwblJSQUIQAA%3D%3D\"],\"https://business.google.com/local/business/14772176348859172102/customers/reviews/deletereply?p\\u003dCiRDaGREU1VoTk1HOW5TMFZKUTBGblNVUlFhMWxQY0hwblJSQUIQAA%3D%3D\",[null,null,null,\"/local/business/14772176348859172102/customers/reviews/deletereply?p\\u003dCiRDaGREU1VoTk1HOW5TMFZKUTBGblNVUlFhMWxQY0hwblJSQUIQAA%3D%3D\"],null,\"https://business.google.com/local/business/14772176348859172102/customers/reviews/reply?p\\u003dCiRDaGREU1VoTk1HOW5TMFZKUTBGblNVUlFhMWxQY0hwblJSQUIQAA%3D%3D\",[null,null,null,\"/local/business/14772176348859172102/customers/reviews/reply?p\\u003dCiRDaGREU1VoTk1HOW5TMFZKUTBGblNVUlFhMWxQY0hwblJSQUIQAA%3D%3D\"],\"https://www.google.com/local/place/review/message?lid\\u003d14772176348859172102\\u0026prspp\\u003dChIJAAAAAAAAAAARRUdquw/5w5USJENoZERTVWhOTUc5blMwVkpRMEZuU1VSUWExbFBjSHBuUlJBQg%3D%3D\\u0026ut\\u003dpr1\\u0026us\\u003dAGDrRGTJfQktsgeC6u2DbOJb48-c\\u0026entry\\u003dugca\"],[null,null,null,[\"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data\\u003d!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURQa1lPcHpnRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x95c3f90fbb6a4745!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgIDPkYOpzgE%7CCgwIvda6ugYQ2JucygE%7C?hl\\u003den-US\"],[\"https://www.google.com/local/review/rap/report?postId\\u003dChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURQa1lPcHpnRRAB\\u0026t\\u003d1\\u0026entityid\\u003dChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURQa1lPcHpnRRItChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURQa1lPcExnEhNDZ3dJdmRhNnVnWVEySnVjeWdFGi4KF0NJSE0wb2dLRUlDQWdJRFBrWU9wcmdFEhNDZ3dJdmRhNnVnWVEySnVjeWdFIhIJAAAAAAAAAAARRUdquw_5w5UqE0Nnd0l2ZGE2dWdZUTJKdWN5Z0U\\u0026wv\\u003d1\\u0026d\\u003d286732320\",null,null,\"0ahUKEwjoh7aZ09eLAxWEl4kEHS94B2QQoykIxAEoCg\"],null,[null,[[1,1]]]],\"0ahUKEwjA8dKZ09
